<plot>When henpecked Arthur's overbearing girlfriend Gwen leaves town for a week, he decides to buy a medieval sword from a television shopping channel. Arthur has so much fun with his new toy that he quickly forgets all about his controlling girlfriend and begins to think of himself for a change. When Gwen returns, however, Arthur must choose between his old life and his new found independence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?485094</url></doc>
